You are his birth mother,

282
00:20:46,740 --> 00:20:48,020
she’s the legal mother.

283
00:20:49,820 --> 00:20:51,580
But Sixth Brother is still young.

284
00:20:52,700 --> 00:20:54,100
= Zhao Heng =
If both of you raise him,

285
00:20:56,420 --> 00:20:57,940
what should he do?

286
00:20:59,180 --> 00:21:02,100
If he didn’t deal with it well,
the court will be in a mess.

287
00:21:02,940 --> 00:21:04,140
And so is the world.

288
00:21:05,580 --> 00:21:07,340
His Majesty came to the Yongding Mausoleum

289
00:21:11,380 --> 00:21:13,460
with only one purpose, to mourn the late Emperor.

290
00:21:27,780 --> 00:21:29,860
In all subordinates’ and people’s heart,

291
00:21:30,820 --> 00:21:32,860
the Empress Dowager and Your Majesty
are loving mother and dutiful son.

292
00:21:33,300 --> 00:21:35,060
Both of you are dedicated to making
the country prosper.

293
00:21:35,940 --> 00:21:38,500
This is the Emperor

294
00:21:39,140 --> 00:21:40,740
for whom they will devote all their energy

295
00:21:41,180 --> 00:21:43,820
and show their appreciation and love.

296
00:21:44,700 --> 00:21:45,580
Loving mother and dutiful son?

297
00:21:45,620 --> 00:21:46,420
What about her?

298
00:21:49,460 --> 00:21:50,300
Your Majesty,

299
00:21:51,620 --> 00:21:53,220
a word please?

300
00:21:54,140 --> 00:21:56,060
This is where former Emperor’s Concubine Li lives.

301
00:21:56,980 --> 00:21:58,780
She stays in the Mausoleum on
the late Emperor’s command.

302
00:21:59,180 --> 00:22:01,660
She has little contact with the world
and meets no guests.

303
00:22:02,540 --> 00:22:04,220
Please do not disturb her.

304
00:22:07,220 --> 00:22:08,460
On the late Emperor’s command?

305
00:22:19,940 --> 00:22:21,300
On the late Emperor’s command?

306
00:22:56,820 --> 00:22:58,700
Has Your Majesty ever thought about

307
00:22:59,380 --> 00:23:00,700
what will happen

308
00:23:01,060 --> 00:23:02,300
if Your Majesty steps in that door

309
00:23:03,460 --> 00:23:04,740
and meets with Concubine Li?

310
00:23:09,060 --> 00:23:12,060
I’ll just do what I should do.

311
00:23:14,260 --> 00:23:15,460
I want to ask you,

312
00:23:16,220 --> 00:23:17,260
if I take her back

313
00:23:17,460 --> 00:23:18,660
to the palace,

314
00:23:19,020 --> 00:23:20,140
and tell the people

315
00:23:20,420 --> 00:23:21,660
both the legal mother and birth mother
will be in the palace,

316
00:23:22,780 --> 00:23:23,780
what will the Empress Dowager do?

317
00:23:24,660 --> 00:23:27,660
What will you do?

318
00:23:29,140 --> 00:23:29,780
Well,

319
00:23:30,140 --> 00:23:31,780
if she does not allow it,

320
00:23:32,180 --> 00:23:33,420
and all vassals support her,

321
00:23:34,020 --> 00:23:35,020
the worst scenario would be no more than

322
00:23:35,140 --> 00:23:36,580
that she takes the full control of the court

323
00:23:36,740 --> 00:23:37,900
without even staying behind the curtain.

324
00:23:39,740 --> 00:23:42,140
Concubine Li won’t go back with you.

325
00:23:42,380 --> 00:23:42,940
How can you know…

326
00:23:42,980 --> 00:23:44,780
The Empress Dowager won’t take the throne, either.

327
00:23:45,100 --> 00:23:48,420
All vassals won’t let it happen to have
another female dictator.

328
00:23:49,260 --> 00:23:52,780
But all vassals should follow the ancestors’ rules

329
00:23:53,020 --> 00:23:54,220
and obey the late Emperor’s command.

330
00:23:54,460 --> 00:23:57,380
He asked Your Majesty to take the throne

331
00:23:57,860 --> 00:23:58,980
the Empress Dowager to assist,

332
00:23:59,540 --> 00:24:01,220
and Concubine Li to stay with the Mausoleum.

333
00:24:10,220 --> 00:24:12,100
What if I insist to bring her back?

334
00:24:13,780 --> 00:24:15,300
Then the Empress Dowager and vassals

335
00:24:15,580 --> 00:24:16,900
will only think that

336
00:24:16,940 --> 00:24:19,220
Your Majesty has been misled by villains,

337
00:24:20,060 --> 00:24:22,660
and is being childish and willful.

338
00:24:22,940 --> 00:24:24,340
Alright, alright,

339
00:24:24,500 --> 00:24:26,260
so what if I am just being childish?

340
00:24:27,300 --> 00:24:28,260
Then

341
00:24:28,900 --> 00:24:31,180
they are more assured that
Your Majesty is still young

342
00:24:31,220 --> 00:24:32,740
and your mental and mind are still immature

343
00:24:32,780 --> 00:24:34,460
that Your Majesty can’t fulfill
the job as an Emperor

344
00:24:35,180 --> 00:24:36,260
so I’ll keep

345
00:24:37,460 --> 00:24:38,940
staying with you and teach you

346
00:24:39,460 --> 00:24:42,260
while political affairs will all be managed
by the Empress Dowager.

347
00:24:42,540 --> 00:24:43,980
When Your Majesty becomes more mature,

348
00:24:44,620 --> 00:24:48,140
the state affairs will be gradually
returned back into your hands.

349
00:24:49,580 --> 00:24:51,220
Okay, okay.

350
00:24:51,620 --> 00:24:52,740
I’m childish,

351
00:24:53,340 --> 00:24:54,940
immature and rebellious.

352
00:24:55,260 --> 00:24:56,460
I do not deserve to be an Emperor.

353
00:24:57,020 --> 00:24:58,140
I quit.

354
00:24:58,420 --> 00:25:00,580
I’m going to break that door right now

355
00:25:00,580 --> 00:25:01,340
and take my mother with me.

356
00:25:01,340 --> 00:25:02,420
I’ll raise her by myself.

357
00:25:20,340 --> 00:25:21,940
Your Majesty.

358
00:25:23,740 --> 00:25:25,140
This is the scripture

359
00:25:25,380 --> 00:25:27,540
Concubine Li wrote for Your Majesty.

360
00:25:28,620 --> 00:25:29,820
She said

361
00:25:30,340 --> 00:25:33,060
she stays with the late Emperor here,

362
00:25:33,060 --> 00:25:34,740
living a calm and peaceful life.

363
00:25:35,300 --> 00:25:37,700
She often hears the maids

364
00:25:37,700 --> 00:25:39,420
talking about

365
00:25:39,820 --> 00:25:42,940
the stable country and society we are in now

366
00:25:43,220 --> 00:25:46,460
ruled by you with the Empress
Concubine’s assistance.

367
00:25:47,180 --> 00:25:50,060
Concubine Li transcribed scriptures all day long,

368
00:25:50,340 --> 00:25:53,460
and finished one scroll in more than a year.

369
00:25:53,860 --> 00:25:58,180
She wants to give it to the Empress
Dowager and Your Majesty.

370
00:25:58,580 --> 00:26:03,100
Wish Your Majesty and the Empress
Dowager stay healthy and happy,

371
00:26:03,580 --> 00:26:08,100
and the country shrive and prosper.

372
00:26:08,780 --> 00:26:10,460
To the Empress Dowager and me?

373
00:26:10,860 --> 00:26:11,740
What else did she say?

374
00:26:12,460 --> 00:26:13,860
She said

375
00:26:14,740 --> 00:26:15,980
your benevolence

376
00:26:16,620 --> 00:26:20,020
will make Your Majesty a good Emperor.

377
00:26:21,540 --> 00:26:24,940
It is a huge blessing to the people

378
00:26:25,420 --> 00:26:28,020
to have Your Majesty protect them.

379
00:26:33,060 --> 00:26:34,340
How can she know I’m benevolent?

380
00:26:36,460 --> 00:26:38,420
A few months ago,

381
00:26:39,540 --> 00:26:41,140
she went to

382
00:26:41,140 --> 00:26:43,020
a temple nearby,

383
00:26:43,700 --> 00:26:44,700
and the abbot told her

384
00:26:45,340 --> 00:26:46,780
the golden crown of Bodhisattva

385
00:26:46,980 --> 00:26:48,620
was stolen few days ago.

386
00:26:49,460 --> 00:26:52,060
When he reported it to the court for rebuilding,

387
00:26:52,580 --> 00:26:54,300
it’s Your Majesty who gave the order

388
00:26:55,100 --> 00:26:58,020
to temples with loose guard

389
00:26:58,300 --> 00:27:01,180
not to use statues made of gold.

390
00:27:04,300 --> 00:27:05,260
I remember this.

391
00:27:06,500 --> 00:27:07,580
I thought

392
00:27:07,980 --> 00:27:09,540
people are not civilized enough

393
00:27:09,860 --> 00:27:10,940
to control their desire.

394
00:27:11,660 --> 00:27:13,180
If the statue is crowned with gold

395
00:27:14,060 --> 00:27:15,100
yet without strict guard

396
00:27:15,380 --> 00:27:16,540
that can’t prevent people from stealing,

397
00:27:17,260 --> 00:27:18,700
it’s enticing them to commit a crime.

398
00:27:19,780 --> 00:27:21,500
If they did so and got punished,

399
00:27:22,020 --> 00:27:23,300
doesn’t this go against

400
00:27:23,300 --> 00:27:24,340
the original purpose of studying the Buddha?

401
00:27:25,300 --> 00:27:28,500
The abbot told what Your Majesty said

402
00:27:28,940 --> 00:27:30,100
to everyone.

403
00:27:31,260 --> 00:27:33,540
They admired Your Majesty deeply.

404
00:27:34,380 --> 00:27:35,420
The abbot said

405
00:27:36,220 --> 00:27:38,980
Your Majesty can not only show
understanding for the weak,

406
00:27:39,660 --> 00:27:41,860
but also forgive the crime

407
00:27:42,220 --> 00:27:44,540
committed by the helpless fool,

408
00:27:44,940 --> 00:27:46,540
that is the spirit of Buddha.

409
00:27:47,500 --> 00:27:50,700
It’s a real blessing

410
00:27:51,780 --> 00:27:53,060
for people

411
00:27:53,500 --> 00:27:55,300
to have an Emperor who treats them
with the spirit of Buddha.

412
00:27:57,900 --> 00:28:01,140
Hearing this, Concubine Li wept for joy.

413
00:28:03,260 --> 00:28:04,820
She hopes Your Majesty

414
00:28:04,820 --> 00:28:07,140
can be an Emperor of benevolence
and spread forth blessings.

415
00:28:07,420 --> 00:28:08,980
This is what

416
00:28:09,380 --> 00:28:11,620
all the vassals and people hoping for.

417
00:28:13,580 --> 00:28:14,500
An Emperor of benevolence.

418
00:28:16,500 --> 00:28:17,140
You explained to me

419
00:28:17,220 --> 00:28:18,780
the Book of Filial Piety word by word.

420
00:28:20,420 --> 00:28:21,940
The filial duty of an Emperor

421
00:28:22,660 --> 00:28:24,540
is to dedicate his love and respect to his parents,

422
00:28:25,420 --> 00:28:28,580
to educate people and rule the country by law.

423
00:28:29,900 --> 00:28:31,060
As the Emperor,

424
00:28:31,620 --> 00:28:33,140
I can’t fulfill my filial duty to my birth mother,

425
00:28:34,220 --> 00:28:35,540
how can I educate people

426
00:28:36,260 --> 00:28:37,540
and be an Emperor of benevolence?

427
00:28:38,660 --> 00:28:41,340
Your Majesty, in the Book of Filial Piety

428
00:28:42,100 --> 00:28:43,620
the Filial duty of an Emperor

429
00:28:44,380 --> 00:28:47,020
is not completely the same with people’s.

430
00:28:47,300 --> 00:28:49,500
How so?

431
00:28:49,860 --> 00:28:52,340
The filial duty of an emperor focuses

432
00:28:52,980 --> 00:28:55,220
on educating

433
00:28:55,580 --> 00:28:57,180
common people

434
00:28:57,540 --> 00:29:00,140
to make people obey the law.

435
00:29:01,060 --> 00:29:02,820
The Empress Dowager spares no effort
in the performance of her duty

436
00:29:03,420 --> 00:29:05,700
and Your Majesty abides by the teaching
of the late Emperor,

437
00:29:06,300 --> 00:29:08,820
attends the court with your mother and
learns to manage affairs of the country.

438
00:29:09,740 --> 00:29:11,580
Your Majesty sets the best example
to all the people by

439
00:29:12,020 --> 00:29:15,700
being the loving mother and dutiful son.

440
00:29:16,980 --> 00:29:18,260
What about my mother

441
00:29:19,500 --> 00:29:20,540
who gave birth to me

442
00:29:21,060 --> 00:29:21,820
but never

443
00:29:21,820 --> 00:29:23,300
had my kneed down tribute?

444
00:29:24,580 --> 00:29:28,100
She gave birth to the Emperor for all the people,

445
00:29:28,460 --> 00:29:31,380
and people are supporting her

446
00:29:31,940 --> 00:29:33,420
for you.

447
00:29:56,900 --> 00:30:02,060
= The Diamond Perfection of Wisdom Sutra =

448
00:30:09,340 --> 00:30:12,260
I heard Concubine Li is ill,

449
00:30:13,180 --> 00:30:14,300
did Physician check her?

450
00:30:15,500 --> 00:30:17,420
Yes, Your Majesty.

451
00:30:18,260 --> 00:30:19,540
He prescribed medicine

452
00:30:19,620 --> 00:30:21,420
and she felt much better after she took it.

453
00:30:27,980 --> 00:30:28,900
Try this.

454
00:30:28,910 --> 00:30:31,060
= Zhao Zhen =

455
00:30:32,500 --> 00:30:33,940
I like you best.

456
00:30:34,060 --> 00:30:36,220
You can make the best candied fruits.

457
00:30:42,740 --> 00:30:45,540
Can’t I go inside just to sit for a while?

458
00:30:46,300 --> 00:30:47,060
Er…

459
00:30:47,060 --> 00:30:48,580
I remember

460
00:30:49,460 --> 00:30:51,660
the candied fruit she made

461
00:30:51,660 --> 00:30:52,660
is the best.

462
00:30:53,700 --> 00:30:56,380
I just want to have a cup of tea

463
00:30:56,900 --> 00:30:59,140
and some candied fruits I had when I was young.

464
00:31:01,220 --> 00:31:05,340
She stopped making desserts or candied fruits

465
00:31:06,980 --> 00:31:10,260
ever since she came here.

466
00:31:13,500 --> 00:31:14,940
If Your Majesty likes those,

467
00:31:16,100 --> 00:31:17,580
I know that

468
00:31:18,660 --> 00:31:22,700
she learned

469
00:31:23,060 --> 00:31:24,660
from Granny Liang

470
00:31:25,860 --> 00:31:28,060
in the dessert shop

471
00:31:28,900 --> 00:31:30,820
before she went to the palace.

472
00:31:37,460 --> 00:31:39,180
= Candied Fruits of Liang =
I thought you are an educated man

473
00:31:39,420 --> 00:31:39,940
and listened to you

474
00:31:39,980 --> 00:31:40,820
talking for so long.

475
00:31:40,900 --> 00:31:41,660
But what you said

476
00:31:42,460 --> 00:31:43,700
is completely bullshit.

477
00:31:44,100 --> 00:31:45,220
You know what,

478
00:31:45,220 --> 00:31:46,420
If you keep importuning

479
00:31:46,420 --> 00:31:47,340
and poking your nose into other’s business,

480
00:31:47,580 --> 00:31:48,940
the stick in my hand

481
00:31:48,940 --> 00:31:50,420
doesn’t give a crap to what you said.

482
00:31:50,420 --> 00:31:51,820
Darling, don’t stop me.

483
00:31:51,820 --> 00:31:52,580
Go inside.

484
00:31:53,780 --> 00:31:54,700
Mr. Han said

485
00:31:54,980 --> 00:31:56,300
= Mrs. Liang =
you can’t go out.

486
00:31:56,300 --> 00:31:57,900
He can manage it himself.

487
00:31:57,900 --> 00:31:58,820
Move.

488
00:31:58,860 --> 00:32:00,340
He said you should rest

489
00:32:00,340 --> 00:32:01,260
after you had the medicine.

490
00:32:01,460 --> 00:32:02,670
= Mr. Liang =

491
00:32:02,700 --> 00:32:04,580
Mr. Han is only a scholar,

492
00:32:04,740 --> 00:32:06,420
how can he deal with those rascals?

493
00:32:07,980 --> 00:32:08,860
I said move!

494
00:32:12,860 --> 00:32:13,980
Move!

495
00:32:15,500 --> 00:32:17,300
I am not poking my nose into other’s business.

496
00:32:17,500 --> 00:32:19,020
= Han Qi =
I am a scholar

497
00:32:19,340 --> 00:32:20,900
who will attend the court someday

498
00:32:20,900 --> 00:32:22,060
to take responsibility for the people.

499
00:32:22,700 --> 00:32:24,340
Though

500
00:32:24,500 --> 00:32:25,940
I only passed the county exam

501
00:32:26,180 --> 00:32:28,140
and there are department exam and
palace exam to go.

502
00:32:28,540 --> 00:32:30,420
But if I don’t help

503
00:32:30,740 --> 00:32:31,780
when I saw villain bullying common people,

504
00:32:31,860 --> 00:32:32,980
how can I be a qualified officer in the future

505
00:32:33,620 --> 00:32:34,500
- Yuansheng. - even if I topped the ranking?

506
00:32:34,740 --> 00:32:36,660
= Granny Liang =
I’m going to help Mr. Han.

507
00:32:37,060 --> 00:32:39,060
Listen to me, you are young.

508
00:32:39,340 --> 00:32:40,100
Don’ go there.

509
00:32:43,780 --> 00:32:44,580
Sir,

510
00:32:44,780 --> 00:32:46,100
today I meet you,

511
00:32:46,580 --> 00:32:48,980
let me tell you the virtue of sages.

512
00:32:50,100 --> 00:32:51,180
Stop nagging.

513
00:32:52,180 --> 00:32:53,100
Listen,

514
00:32:53,180 --> 00:32:54,060
listen,

515
00:33:00,620 --> 00:33:02,380
if I hit you and hurt you,

516
00:33:03,340 --> 00:33:04,100
you will definitely show your wound

517
00:33:04,180 --> 00:33:05,460
ten days later

518
00:33:05,500 --> 00:33:06,340
in your exam

519
00:33:06,340 --> 00:33:07,300
to all the officials.

520
00:33:08,100 --> 00:33:08,940
You will make a big thing out of it

521
00:33:08,940 --> 00:33:10,340
so that His Majesty will know.

522
00:33:10,860 --> 00:33:12,460
Well, I won’t beat you

523
00:33:12,460 --> 00:33:14,020
or hurt you.

524
00:33:19,180 --> 00:33:20,140
If you want,

525
00:33:20,380 --> 00:33:21,820
you can go to attend the exam with a bad smell

526
00:33:22,260 --> 00:33:24,580
after ten days without a shower.

527
00:33:31,060 --> 00:33:32,940
None of you can leave.

528
00:33:34,300 --> 00:33:35,140
Notify the local government.

529
00:33:35,300 --> 00:33:37,140
No, we can’t.

530
00:33:38,580 --> 00:33:39,300
What?

531
00:33:39,980 --> 00:33:41,140
You look like an educated man,

532
00:33:41,700 --> 00:33:43,340
are you the one

533
00:33:43,780 --> 00:33:44,620
who’s bullying others?

534
00:33:44,900 --> 00:33:46,140
How can it be me?

535
00:33:46,580 --> 00:33:47,940
I’m just a scholar

536
00:33:48,300 --> 00:33:49,860
without families like you.

537
00:33:50,300 --> 00:33:51,780
I was almost wetted by the food waste

538
00:33:51,780 --> 00:33:53,180
for helping the weak.

539
00:33:54,060 --> 00:33:55,620
Then why don’t you notify the local government?

540
00:33:56,460 --> 00:33:57,460
Because

541
00:33:57,820 --> 00:33:59,020
the source of bullying

542
00:33:59,060 --> 00:34:00,220
are not those villains,

543
00:34:00,980 --> 00:34:02,580
but the superior of all the officials,

544
00:34:02,900 --> 00:34:04,140
the Emperor of Song.

545
00:34:13,820 --> 00:34:15,420
This is the House of Liang

546
00:34:15,500 --> 00:34:16,980
who’s famous for its candied fruits?

547
00:34:17,900 --> 00:34:19,940
Come on, I’ll buy you some tea and dessert,

548
00:34:20,140 --> 00:34:22,500
and you can tell me how the Emperor of Song

549
00:34:22,580 --> 00:34:24,140
becomes the source of bullying?

550
00:34:29,420 --> 00:34:31,100
Relax, I’m not an official,

551
00:34:31,340 --> 00:34:32,340
and I didn’t pass any exam.

552
00:34:33,020 --> 00:34:34,100
But I have someone in my family

553
00:34:34,100 --> 00:34:35,060
who has some power.

554
00:34:35,540 --> 00:34:36,740
If what you say makes sense,

555
00:34:36,980 --> 00:34:39,180
I’ll let my family to protect this shop

556
00:34:39,700 --> 00:34:41,660
from villains.

557
00:34:44,300 --> 00:34:45,940
Sir, please come in.

558
00:34:45,940 --> 00:34:49,340
Come in, come in please.

559
00:34:49,340 --> 00:34:50,620
Go, serve the guests.

560
00:34:50,980 --> 00:34:52,340
- Come in, have a seat. - Okay.

561
00:34:52,380 --> 00:34:53,140
Please, come in.

562
00:34:55,060 --> 00:34:56,780
Please sit here.

563
00:35:08,780 --> 00:35:10,180
Mr. Zhu is a notorious villain here

564
00:35:10,260 --> 00:35:10,580
who’s blackmailing

565
00:35:10,660 --> 00:35:12,340
shop owners.

566
00:35:12,940 --> 00:35:14,460
Why the victim who’s been blackmailed

567
00:35:14,460 --> 00:35:15,340
can’t notify the local government

568
00:35:15,780 --> 00:35:16,580
is because the Emperor

569
00:35:16,620 --> 00:35:18,420
forbids to run shops in residential area.

570
00:35:18,740 --> 00:35:19,700
If they notify the local government

571
00:35:19,780 --> 00:35:21,820
even if the villain is arrested,

572
00:35:22,100 --> 00:35:23,660
they can’t run the shop anymore

573
00:35:23,700 --> 00:35:24,740
and they’ll get punished.

574
00:35:25,900 --> 00:35:28,340
The government is more merciless than villains.

575
00:35:30,140 --> 00:35:32,300
What you said doesn’t make sense.

576
00:35:33,300 --> 00:35:35,180
Villains who conduct crimes should be punished,

577
00:35:35,500 --> 00:35:36,900
but not people

578
00:35:37,420 --> 00:35:38,820
who run a shop against the rule?

579
00:35:39,780 --> 00:35:41,380
The government maintains the law

580
00:35:41,380 --> 00:35:42,340
and handles things accordingly,

581
00:35:43,180 --> 00:35:44,500
but you call it merciless.

582
00:35:45,700 --> 00:35:46,540
You learnt this

583
00:35:46,700 --> 00:35:48,940
from the books?

584
00:35:49,580 --> 00:35:51,700
Are you from

585
00:35:51,740 --> 00:35:52,820
the fairyland?

586
00:35:55,020 --> 00:35:56,020
What are you talking about?

587
00:36:03,180 --> 00:36:05,660
You are here just to make fun of me?

588
00:36:07,420 --> 00:36:09,380
From your dressing and manners, I assume

589
00:36:09,980 --> 00:36:11,820
you must be born in a civilized family

590
00:36:11,820 --> 00:36:12,780
and educated with poems and fine arts.

591
00:36:13,340 --> 00:36:14,140
Aren’t you from the fairyland

592
00:36:14,180 --> 00:36:15,780
compared with those

593
00:36:16,020 --> 00:36:17,180
who work so hard

594
00:36:17,180 --> 00:36:19,180
all day long

595
00:36:19,860 --> 00:36:20,780
yet can’t even

596
00:36:20,860 --> 00:36:22,180
earn a living for their family?

597
00:36:23,260 --> 00:36:24,500
How can you understand

598
00:36:24,940 --> 00:36:26,420
that they have no choice

599
00:36:26,860 --> 00:36:28,540
but to break the rule just to make a living?

600
00:36:28,660 --> 00:36:29,500
Are you telling…

601
00:36:30,780 --> 00:36:31,540
Telling me

602
00:36:32,580 --> 00:36:33,780
that people have no way of making a living in Song?

603
00:36:39,620 --> 00:36:41,460
Grinding tea, and two dishes of biscuits.

604
00:36:41,860 --> 00:36:43,300
It’s a dish of fresh fruit

605
00:36:43,340 --> 00:36:44,580
for you.

606
00:36:45,100 --> 00:36:46,940
Try it first, if you want anything else,

607
00:36:46,940 --> 00:36:48,220
granny and my mother will make them immediately.

608
00:36:49,580 --> 00:36:50,420
You’re seven years old now.

609
00:36:50,860 --> 00:36:52,780
Are you not going to school but
just helping in the shop?

610
00:36:53,180 --> 00:36:54,500
You forgot again, Brother Han,

611
00:36:54,820 --> 00:36:56,180
I’m seven years and one month old.

612
00:36:56,460 --> 00:36:58,020
My father teaches me too,

613
00:36:58,660 --> 00:36:59,980
but he became sick

614
00:37:00,060 --> 00:37:00,980
for preparing the department exam.

615
00:37:01,460 --> 00:37:02,620
He even spit out blood.

616
00:37:03,060 --> 00:37:04,500
My mother just gave birth to my young brother.

617
00:37:04,980 --> 00:37:05,460
So I’m helping granny

618
00:37:05,500 --> 00:37:06,700
to manage the shop.

619
00:37:07,460 --> 00:37:09,540
How can you handle it at your age?

620
00:37:10,140 --> 00:37:11,220
Usually it’s OK.

621
00:37:11,980 --> 00:37:13,900
But today that villain came

622
00:37:14,500 --> 00:37:16,260
and scared all the customers away.

623
00:37:17,060 --> 00:37:18,620
Granny dared not to open the business

624
00:37:19,380 --> 00:37:20,300
and my mother

625
00:37:20,340 --> 00:37:22,060
didn’t have time to prepare

626
00:37:22,220 --> 00:37:23,620
our best candied fruits.

627
00:38:04,460 --> 00:38:05,700
You must’ve waited for long.

628
00:38:05,740 --> 00:38:06,580
Come on,

629
00:38:07,460 --> 00:38:08,220
here we go

630
00:38:08,660 --> 00:38:11,580
try some plum snow cake.

631
00:38:11,860 --> 00:38:12,860
Come on, have some.

632
00:38:14,300 --> 00:38:14,980
Come on.

633
00:38:15,460 --> 00:38:16,700
Mille Feuille

634
00:38:16,700 --> 00:38:17,740
with candied plums

635
00:38:17,780 --> 00:38:19,140
needs a bit longer.

636
00:38:19,580 --> 00:38:21,260
That takes more time.

637
00:38:21,780 --> 00:38:24,260
Before, we had a lot of customers

638
00:38:24,260 --> 00:38:25,900
and that desert was always on the table.

639
00:38:26,780 --> 00:38:28,660
So we would start to prepare it
first in the morning.

640
00:38:29,420 --> 00:38:30,220
Please.

641
00:38:38,900 --> 00:38:39,900
Are you wondering

642
00:38:40,420 --> 00:38:42,260
why did not they open the shop in the market?

643
00:38:43,380 --> 00:38:44,700
They have five people in the family,

644
00:38:45,060 --> 00:38:46,740
you’ve seen the old and the young,

645
00:38:47,140 --> 00:38:48,700
and look at that couple.

646
00:38:58,340 --> 00:38:59,220
I’ll do it myself.

647
00:38:59,300 --> 00:39:02,060
= Liang Yuanheng =

648
00:39:02,860 --> 00:39:03,660
Come on,

649
00:39:05,900 --> 00:39:06,700
lie down.

650
00:39:32,740 --> 00:39:33,620
Look at them.

651
00:39:34,420 --> 00:39:35,700
Who can get up early

652
00:39:36,300 --> 00:39:37,420
and send all the materials

653
00:39:37,460 --> 00:39:38,820
to the market in the early morning?

654
00:39:39,300 --> 00:39:40,180
The granny?

655
00:39:40,780 --> 00:39:42,580
Or the man who’s being sick for years?

656
00:39:43,180 --> 00:39:44,100
That’s why I said

657
00:39:44,380 --> 00:39:45,460
the source of bullying

658
00:39:45,460 --> 00:39:46,740
is not those villains.

659
00:39:47,500 --> 00:39:48,220
Does it make sense to you

660
00:39:48,220 --> 00:39:49,780
when I say it’s because of

661
00:39:49,980 --> 00:39:51,100
the superior of all the officials?

662
00:39:53,180 --> 00:39:54,140
You said just now,

663
00:39:54,380 --> 00:39:55,620
if I explained it clearly to you,

664
00:39:55,620 --> 00:39:56,260
and if it makes sense,

665
00:39:56,420 --> 00:39:57,580
you’ll let your family

666
00:39:57,580 --> 00:39:58,980
deal with the villain Zhu,

667
00:39:59,260 --> 00:40:00,620
and protect Liang from him.

668
00:40:00,620 --> 00:40:02,500
I mean what I say.

669
00:40:03,020 --> 00:40:04,980
But since you hate the court so much,

670
00:40:05,020 --> 00:40:07,100
hate the Emperor so much,

671
00:40:07,500 --> 00:40:08,940
why do you attend the exam,
trying to be an official?

672
00:40:09,300 --> 00:40:10,220
Do you want to get into the court

673
00:40:10,220 --> 00:40:13,100
and earn a share?

674
00:40:13,420 --> 00:40:14,340
Of course not.

675
00:40:15,020 --> 00:40:16,620
His Majesty is responsible for the state

676
00:40:16,820 --> 00:40:18,500
and the masses.

677
00:40:18,820 --> 00:40:19,180
I don’t believe

678
00:40:19,220 --> 00:40:20,620
he really doesn’t care about his people.

679
00:40:21,100 --> 00:40:21,900
It’s not because he doesn’t care,

680
00:40:21,980 --> 00:40:22,860
but because he doesn’t know.

681
00:40:23,420 --> 00:40:24,660
Those high officials

682
00:40:25,300 --> 00:40:27,420
only say nice things and flatter him,

683
00:40:27,540 --> 00:40:28,460
praising the peace and prosperity.

684
00:40:29,020 --> 00:40:29,980
How much can he hear

685
00:40:30,180 --> 00:40:31,900
about the difficulties of the people?

686
00:40:32,420 --> 00:40:33,620
I despise the officials,

687
00:40:33,660 --> 00:40:34,740
that’s why I must be one.

688
00:40:35,820 --> 00:40:37,740
If I can be selected to attend the court,

689
00:40:37,900 --> 00:40:39,260
I may not be qualified to make great contributions,

690
00:40:39,580 --> 00:40:41,260
but I should never deceive my
superior and inferior.

691
00:41:04,220 --> 00:41:05,620
Do you know how

692
00:41:05,620 --> 00:41:06,700
our first Emperor dealt with

693
00:41:06,980 --> 00:41:07,460
the injunction issued in the Tang Dynasty

694
00:41:07,500 --> 00:41:08,700
to separate the market and the residence?

695
00:41:09,260 --> 00:41:10,500
I don’t recall it has been abolished.

696
00:41:10,980 --> 00:41:12,540
The first Emperors didn’t punish people

697
00:41:12,660 --> 00:41:14,220
for opening shops in their residence,

698
00:41:14,260 --> 00:41:15,180
is that true?

699
00:41:16,340 --> 00:41:17,220
Your Majesty,

700
00:41:17,340 --> 00:41:19,220
didn’t you go there to buy candied fruits
and desserts?

701
00:41:24,620 --> 00:41:26,420
Your majesty, dinner is ready.

702
00:41:26,500 --> 00:41:27,980
Elbow meat and smoked fish are cold dishes.

703
00:41:28,180 --> 00:41:29,900
Roasted lamb stays warm with a gentle heat.

704
00:41:30,100 --> 00:41:31,380
I’ll bring you

705
00:41:31,380 --> 00:41:32,900
the fish rice soup from the kitchen.

706
00:41:33,340 --> 00:41:35,020
= Diligent and cautious from morning to night =
Nothing else?

707
00:41:36,500 --> 00:41:38,220
Your Majesty doesn’t want lamb today?

708
00:41:38,780 --> 00:41:39,740
I’ll ask now.

709
00:41:39,860 --> 00:41:40,900
We should still have some

710
00:41:40,900 --> 00:41:41,660
Tibet pork we got yesterday.

711
00:41:41,660 --> 00:41:42,500
I’m not talking about pork,

712
00:41:43,100 --> 00:41:45,740
I’m asking if there’s anything else important?

713
00:41:46,580 --> 00:41:48,620
What important things are you talking about?

714
00:41:49,620 --> 00:41:51,460
Like the epidemic in the capital

715
00:41:51,620 --> 00:41:52,540
and the flood in Qingzhou.

716
00:41:52,860 --> 00:41:54,580
Didn’t Prime Minister Lv submit anything?

717
00:41:54,780 --> 00:41:56,220
Empress Dowager summoned the
Prime Ministers Lv and Wang

718
00:41:56,260 --> 00:41:57,620
to discuss about the disaster relief in
the Hall of Treasure and Compassion.

719
00:41:58,140 --> 00:41:59,140
But today Your Majesty should

720
00:41:59,180 --> 00:42:00,260
attend Mr. Yan’s lecture

721
00:42:00,460 --> 00:42:01,660
in the Hall of Politics.

722
00:42:02,260 --> 00:42:04,460
So she didn’t ask Your Majesty to join.

723
00:42:07,660 --> 00:42:08,540
Take away the dinner.

724
00:42:09,580 --> 00:42:10,420
You can all leave.

725
00:42:10,820 --> 00:42:11,700
No one can come in.

726
00:42:12,500 --> 00:42:13,220
Yes, Your Majesty.

727
00:42:41,200 --> 00:42:50,860
♪ Loved you a gentleman yet got abandoned ♪

728
00:42:52,200 --> 00:43:00,540
♪ Peach blossoms color the city ♪

729
00:43:03,380 --> 00:43:08,100
♪ Spring breeze purified dusty memories ♪

730
00:43:09,080 --> 00:43:13,240
♪ The gate of the vast palace opens ♪

731
00:43:14,680 --> 00:43:20,160
♪ Bid farewell with wine after the glory ends ♪

732
00:43:20,160 --> 00:43:24,950
♪ Outside the city a beautiful world unveils ♪

733
00:43:28,610 --> 00:43:34,250
♪ Long-standing distance doesn’t alienate us ♪

734
00:43:34,250 --> 00:43:39,160
♪ Keep you company behind the gate ♪

735
00:43:39,660 --> 00:43:45,420
♪ Four seasons come and go ♪

736
00:43:45,420 --> 00:43:50,510
♪ We only have each other in this cage ♪

737
00:43:50,940 --> 00:43:55,870
♪ Wish to fly freely in the next life ♪

738
00:43:56,490 --> 00:44:01,340
♪ Willows turn green flowers red ♪

739
00:44:02,030 --> 00:44:07,180
♪ Sing aloud with wine ♪

740
00:44:07,680 --> 00:44:12,720
♪ Hold your hands and go home together ♪

741
00:44:13,260 --> 00:44:17,330
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

742
00:44:18,800 --> 00:44:23,440
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

743
00:44:24,460 --> 00:44:29,620
♪ The howling wind ♪

744
00:44:29,990 --> 00:44:34,060
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

745
00:44:35,540 --> 00:44:40,460
♪ Be a pair of swallows in the next life ♪

746
00:44:41,120 --> 00:44:46,340
♪ Build the nest and protect the nestlings ♪

747
00:44:46,760 --> 00:44:52,040
♪ The howling wind ♪

748
00:44:52,330 --> 00:44:57,230
♪ Woke me up from the dream ♪

749
00:44:57,820 --> 00:45:04,530
♪ Life is long yet joy is little ♪
